name: Baby Vita Cropped Sweater Black
description:
- Classic fit.
- Crew-neck
- Raglan sleeves with banded knit cuffs start at elbows for added flair.
- Asymmetrical banded hemline.
- Solid glitter printed fabric for extra detailing and style. 
- Measures 16'' from shoulder to front, 19'' from shoulder to back  hemline.
-  60% cotton/ 21% nylon/ 15% polyester/ 4% spandex 
- Pullover style.
- Hand Wash. 
- Made in USA.
